Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:12.14,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,Living your life is a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:16.30,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,But one step ahead,\NI hear there's only darkness.
