Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard\Nthe name Yoshizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:40.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He runs a club in\NRoppongi as a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:44.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The master-tape was\Nstolen from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:48.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're desperately trying\Nto get the tape back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:52.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:56.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:04.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter...\N...who you started a war with!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...who you started a war with!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:11.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands behind\Nyour heads and get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanoh. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a lot of patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make me wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start by cutting off her ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'll chop her up till\Nshe doesn't even look human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you're told!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There, you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:53.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let Mika...\NLet my daughter go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:56.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has nothing to do with thi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:00.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already\Nlost the plot, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:05.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one who got innocent\Npeople involved to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good, Kanoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:22.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lost his mind to sex\Nand money, he can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:27.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Let's make this\Na movie party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:32.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let your daughter see\Nyou in all of your glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see my face, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do that\Nwhen we're editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all over the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:49.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The image of you fondling\Na boy and drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the master-tape\Nor the money, so don't say anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you Yoshizumi,\Nthis is all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going\Nto do about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:04.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a fool to go along\Nwith a dimwit's stupid plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:05.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just...\NShut up you worthless politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:12.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:46.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:49.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...really hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:16.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:24.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make\Nhim suffer like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:35.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten\Nwhat he put us through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what would've\Nhappened if I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...get here when I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...really doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...have anything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And he...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:12.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't hurt my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is her precious father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:23.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:52.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A politician, through and through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:45.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep him alive\Nso long as he's useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and show some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is\Ngood enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:25.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:45.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being touched by me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:08.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to make you feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:19.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...\NIf you don't want me around, I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want me around, I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:27.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:34.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I say something now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what will come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:05.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need anything, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:16.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:28.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...\NDon't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,P-please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:39.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I dragged you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there'll\Nbe any side effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:16.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I trying\Nto say just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,After all the rejections...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:33.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:39.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm depending on him\Nbecause of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:50.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:02.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:10.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing you said or did has\Nanything to do with who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:17.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...know that this is all\Nbecause of a horrible man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:28.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to\Nfeel bad or ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you think, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:20.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't dislike me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:28.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not,\Nwhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...see me at my worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:45.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, those are my lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:46.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:47.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NHuh nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a little\Nlate for this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:55.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hundreds of times\Nworse than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:02.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just said\NI wasn't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were nice to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:11.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:21.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was mad at myself for not\Nbeing able to say it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:27.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,With me beforehand...\NNot even that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:06.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...everything is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the shell\NI've been hiding in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:17.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain goes with it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:22.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't get rid of the\Ndoubts or the confusion, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:44.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to pick\Na fight with me, Gion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:46.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't like sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought them for you, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:55.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're in worse\Nshape than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about him, Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:16:00.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This idiot is a glutton for punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:00.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This idiot is a glutton for punishment.\NYep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:03.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise I wouldn't\Nsurvive hanging out with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...immoral, corrupt money lenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:17.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:19.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Another cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:30.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how\Ndifferent things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:30.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:33.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, it would\Nhave been unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:40.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he's more humane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's your influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering his\Nline of work, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:49.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not sure if\Nit's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still like him\Nbetter this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:03.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking\Nabout me, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... er...\NWe were! We were!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:12.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,About how much you like Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Gion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:17.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just getting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Little late, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:31.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To be told in front\Nof other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:38.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't just\Nget it too, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:41.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:43.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:50.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes were blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:54.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am as sorry as the\Nocean is deep for saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I didn't want to film\NLoveless hanky-panky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, you two,\Nhere's one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:11.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, let me capture\Nsome loving hanky-panky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it look really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it won't\Nget out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only for the personal\Npursuit of beautiful aesthetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could knock this\Ndoor down in one kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:38.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'd do it for\Nthree hundred million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:44.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aya, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:52.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No Money
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No Money\NSide Story
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:02.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking\Nabout, President Kanoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dressed up, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:19.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proving how serious I am. Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:23.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come again to request\Nthat you be in my video!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:27.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just take a\Nglance at the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:35.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I may say so myself,\Nit's a good, heart-felt story!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:39.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit, I don't have\Nthree million to pay you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Money isn't everything, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you'll do it for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a man, Aya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:52.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The time period is\Nthe Taisho-era?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Taisho-era.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:59.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A cold-hearted banker and a young\Nman whose nobility is crumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:02.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's their tragic love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:07.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Loan shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,With money he swindled...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't dawdle! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:19.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there were things\Nyou were good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no accounting\Nfor people's tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he will erase\Nour debt in exchange for...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...a part barbarian mutt like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been a weight\Naround the family's neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:41.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...and now you get to pay\Nus back for bringing you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:48.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they are waiting\Nfor you in the back room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:50.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ayase Yukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:11.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:18.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not here\Nas an employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:31.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time\Nwhen they connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...because of the trap\Nthat Kanoh set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:37.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Ayase,\Nwhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to save everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:42.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They sold you to\Npay back their debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be, but\Nthis is too horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was always your\Nintention to ruin the Ishii's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Ken Ishii was\Nforced into filing bankruptcy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:54.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:57.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They all deserve to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:59.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Their relationship took a turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:47.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of it is about breaking him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:48.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of it is about breaking him in!\NWhat's so heartfelt about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:49.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so heartfelt about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:52.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a story that hits the heart\Nand the groin. It's a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:53.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:53.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:57.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, how are you going\Nto shoot a period piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:22:58.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a cent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:22:59.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:00.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend it to me.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:01.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejection
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:01.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:02.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Proposal\NAnd this storyline is awfully familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:04.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And this storyline is awfully familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:07.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:09.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Edo-style confinement, obi's, woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:12.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could do that\Nwhenever I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:17.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you prefer something\Nthat is totally fantastical?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:20.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:24.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let me film you,\NI'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:27.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you want, in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:39.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:40.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:54.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:03.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a scene from\Nyour fantastical scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:05.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mr. Kanoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.21,0:24:09.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this for an\Nunrealistic situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:24.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Money, money, money, money...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.60,0:24:34.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And all of these Aya's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.18,0:24:48.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...love Mr. Kanoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.02,0:24:56.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh, Mr. Kanoh,\NMr. Kanoh, Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.13,0:25:06.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is it that unlikely\Nthat Ayase would like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.77,0:25:09.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was totally wrong right\Nfrom the "Money, money!" part.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.81,0:25:14.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought it was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.04,0:25:19.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-well, let me hear\Nwhat you want, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.98,0:25:20.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.18,0:25:23.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not necessarily\Ngoing to get made.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.55,0:25:25.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me what you'd want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.89,0:25:27.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.69,0:25:29.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.93,0:25:33.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.17,0:25:38.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.40,0:25:41.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were at school late!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.20,0:25:44.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(319,126)}Youngest Brother\NToranosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.00,0:25:42.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:44.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,424)}Middle Brother Homare
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:44.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(554,386)}Eldest Brother\NMisao
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.17,0:25:44.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What nice brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.91,0:25:46.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.91,0:25:49.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight we're having\Nyour favorite, hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.44,0:25:50.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(473,328)}Mother\NSomeya
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.68,0:25:50.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A loving mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.11,0:25:54.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go wash your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.65,0:25:57.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and get your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.45,0:25:58.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.49,0:26:01.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.46,0:26:03.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.06,0:26:08.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(183,292)}Kitty\N$250,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.49,0:26:08.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,130)}Father\NSomuku Kanoh
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.20,0:26:13.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who's the father, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.77,0:26:17.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then, I'll break\Nyou in the old school way!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.94,0:26:19.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.17,0:26:21.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a turn of events!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.78,0:26:23.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.05,0:26:24.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.85,0:26:27.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The father sexually\Nabuses the fourth son!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.25,0:26:31.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the oldest and\Nsecond sons join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.45,0:26:33.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The mother is a transvestite!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.19,0:26:35.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an adult film that\Ncuts to the heart of...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.19,0:26:37.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...societal issues\Nsurrounding the modern family!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.06,0:26:39.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the title!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.23,0:26:40.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy's Sex Ed
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:42.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy's Sex Ed\NDaddy's Sex Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.10,0:26:43.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.20,0:26:45.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rejection
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.83,0:26:49.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.71,0:26:56.14,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,When I opened the window\Nand spoke to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.21,0:27:02.62,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I could see that the\Nwintry, night sky was sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.75,0:27:08.42,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the emotions\Nof all the people everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.49,0:27:15.02,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...had turned into those stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.23,0:27:22.03,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,That promise we made so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.37,0:27:27.36,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...is something I still\Ncling tightly to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.68,0:27:36.74,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,On sleepless nights in my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.02,0:27:46.05,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a single tear falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.13,0:27:52.07,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never forget that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.37,0:28:03.97,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved, just keep me warm forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.68,0:28:10.31,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm caught\Nin a rainfall of grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.38,0:28:17.42,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to become your love.
